Classes
Class
Description
Aid
Stores aid name, aid quantity and status
AllAid
Used to store all the aid data from aids.csv file Including matched and unmatched aids
DC
A distribution center representing the type of matching of aids donated and received from the donors and NGOs Type of aids matching consists of 1-to-1, 1-to-many, many-to-1, many-to-many
DonatedAid
Used to store the donated aid made by the Donor
Donor
Act as Usertype of donor and store the required details of donor Such as donor name and donor phone number
Main
Main class for the javafx application program GUI for Aid Distribution System Inherited from the Application superclass
NGO

NGOComparator
Used as a compartor for queue by comparing the ngo manpower count
RequestedAid
Used to store the requested aid made by the ngos
TableViewHelper
A class that is created to ease the creation of table in javafx Using javafx Table to show the aids matching of the aid distribution system
User
Use for constructing usertype of donor and ngo Stores the user login info such as username and password
